data.description: This house is a hidden gem in the heart of Jonesboro. Classic brick chimney and a screened in porch help make this house a place to cozy up or entertain. A large, shady side yard is included in the price of the home. Kitchen has been updated with granite countertops, double ovens, and a glass subway backsplash. Original built-ins throughout the house and a wood burning fireplace with a gas insert infuse the home with a sense of 1950s charm. With a one car garage, 1 bedroom and bonus room upstairs, 2 bedrooms downstairs, 2 living areas on the main floor, 2 full bathes, and original hardwood floors throughout, this house is too good to miss! Main floor of house to be painted Benjamin Moore color white dove throughout starting 9/15/2023
